{"type": "article", "id": 12555, "title": "来自自行车零件的躺椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-24T08:08:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122508cgvR64L180GEsfkZ.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\t“Retire” Chair by Matthias Kirchner\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Matthias Kirchner 最近用两辆退休的自行车零件做了一把新的休闲躺椅，其中椅架部分来自自行车的车架，而靠垫部分来自自行车的轮胎，全部手工编织而成，既充分利用旧材料，又能够舒适地贴合使用者的后背。这是<a href=\"http://www.matthias-kirchner.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看他的更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261402503ETClP2JZUzvWHAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261402509qSZ8bMcPxfNT4AY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140251gzDk3WilOuLEJehp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140252qGF9g80BcntaK35m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261402522AqpR1lh3UcNK5bF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140253SabFds04Noe3rxRU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}